PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777169008
OL,3,CFormer X-Factor star faces murder
OL,4,Ccharge after influencer hit by car in
OL,5,CSoho
OL,7,FFormer X Factor finalist Gabrielle
OL,8,FCarrington, 29, appeared in court on
OL,9,FTuesday accused of trying to kill Ms
OL,10,FZakrzewska, a TikTok and Instagram
OL,11,Finfluencer known by the name of
OL,12,FKlaudiaglam, outside the Inca
OL,13,Fnightclub.
OL,15,FThe attempted murder charge will be
OL,16,Fincreased to murder after Ms
OL,17,FZakrzewska's death, the Metropolitan
OL,18,FPolice said on Saturday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
