CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777169008
OL,3,CFormer X-Factor star faces murder
OL,4,Ccharge after influencer hit by car in
OL,5,CSoho
OL,7,FCarrington, of Broadfield Road,
OL,8,FManchester, is also accused of
OL,9,Fdangerous driving, being nearly twice
OL,10,Fthe drink-drive limit and causing
OL,11,Finjuries to two other people ` a third
OL,12,Fwoman and a security guard ` who were
OL,13,Falso hit by her Mercedes.
OL,15,FA 58-year-old man suffered life-
OL,16,Fchanging injuries after being hit by
OL,17,Fthe car.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
