PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777169008
OL,3,CFormer X-Factor star faces murder
OL,4,Ccharge after influencer hit by car in
OL,5,CSoho
OL,7,FShe did not enter any pleas during the
OL,8,Fhearing and will next appear at the
OL,9,FOld Bailey on May 19.
OL,11,FFamily and friends of Ms Zakrzewska
OL,12,Falso attended the court hearing.
OL,14,FNearly #18,000 had been crowdfunded
OL,15,Ffor Ms Zakrzewska's treatment and her
OL,16,Ffamily's legal fees.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
