PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777169008
OL,3,CFormer X-Factor star faces murder
OL,4,Ccharge after influencer hit by car in
OL,5,CSoho
OL,7,FThe GoFundMe, said to be set up by her
OL,8,Fmother, said: "If at any time things
OL,9,Ftake a turn for the worst, additional
OL,10,Ffunds will go towards funeral costs
OL,11,Fand continuous support for the family."
OL,13,FHer mother, Kinga, said on the page:
OL,14,F"Those who know me understand how much
OL,15,FI love my daughter and what a special
OL,16,Fbond we have, and I cannot give up on
OL,17,Fmy baby girl."
OL,26,@pD@OOUsD@gO]vD@AOUyD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
