OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777169008
OL,3,CFormer X-Factor star faces murder
OL,4,Ccharge after influencer hit by car in
OL,5,CSoho
OL,7,FShe added: "Anyone who knew my
OL,8,Fgorgeous daughter knows how truly
OL,9,Fwonderful she is. She has touched so
OL,10,Fmany people with her pure heart and
OL,11,Fkindness, and she deserves every
OL,12,Fchance to keep fighting."
OL,14,FFootage of the incident circulating
OL,15,Fonline shows a woman getting into a
OL,16,Fblack car before it surges forward,
OL,17,Fstriking Ms Zakrzewska who goes under
OL,18,Fthe vehicle.
OL,26,@oD@LOUtD@YO]
