OL,3,CFormer X-Factor star faces murder
OL,4,Ccharge after influencer hit by car in
OL,5,CSoho
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FDetective Chief Inspector Alison
OL,13,FFoxwell, who is leading the
OL,14,Finvestigation, said: "We would like to
OL,15,Fexpress our deepest sympathies to
OL,16,FKlaudia's family and friends in light
OL,17,Fof this tragic update.
OL,19,F"Our thoughts are also with everyone
OL,20,Fimpacted by this incident.
OL,26,@vD@VOU{D@AOU
