OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777169008
OL,3,CFormer X-Factor star faces murder
OL,4,Ccharge after influencer hit by car in
OL,5,CSoho
OL,7,F"We recognise that this case has
OL,8,Fgenerated significant interest and
OL,9,Fdiscussion on social media; however,
OL,10,Fwe would urge the public to refrain
OL,11,Ffrom further speculation."
OL,13,FShe added: "We also ask that people do
OL,14,Fnot share graphic footage out of
OL,15,Frespect for Klaudia's loved ones and
OL,16,Ffor those who have been injured.
OL,18,F"The circulation of such material
OL,19,Fcould also undermine our ongoing
OL,20,Fcriminal investigation and potentially
OL,21,Fprejudice future court proceedings."
